*-------------------------------
*   BUK.DOC
*-------------------------------
*   BUK = Beep Until Keypress
*-------------------------------

    BUK is a utility which will cause a series of 3 beeps to be
    continuously repeated until any key is pressed.

    Its primary purpose is to get the operators attention during the
    execution of a particular segment of a batch file


